  "text": "The dressed states population can be obtained as Now, we are interested in studying the DEM for V-type atomic system by numerically solving equations (3) and [CITATION_1] . It is assumed that the multi-photon resonance condition is fulfilled. All frequency parameters are scaled by γ 1 , which is in the order of MHz for the chosen atomic system. We consider different intensity profiles, i.e., Gaussian and LG modes for the applied fields and investigate steady-state behavior of the DEM in different points of atomic vapor cell. Figure 2 shows the DEM as a function of x for the applied Gaussian fields,",
